login manager. In KDM for example: Click the <em>Session Type<\/em> option and select <em>KDE 4<\/em>, then proceed with the usual login steps.\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><em>kdeplasma-addons<\/em> contains new Plasma fun.<\/p>\n<p>Thanks to Harald, Jon, Steve, Guillaume for preparing these packages.<br \/>\nSpecial thanks to Scott for doing a late night shift to get emergency uploads into Kubuntu Intrepid Alpha 5.<\/p>\n<p>If you want to see your name above, then join the Kubuntu Team.<br \/>\nMore information is available in the <a href=\"https:\/\/wiki.kubuntu.org\/Kubuntu\">Kubuntu Wiki<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>KDE 4.1.1 has been released and packages are available for Kubuntu 8.04, the Hardy Heron. These packages install to \/usr\/lib\/kde4 and can be installed along side your existing KDE 3 installation. Instructions The updated packages for Kubuntu 8.04 are located in the Kubuntu Member&#8217;s KDE 4 Personal Package Archive (PPA)&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":1129,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[129],"tags":[142,144,178],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/711"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=711"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/711\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1512,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/711\/revisions\/1512"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1129"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/kubuntu.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?paren